"title": "4528: trees",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4528: trees",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Large, woody plants with trunk, branches, leaves and roots, noted for their long lives. Scripture refers to many different varieties of tree.</p>\n<h2>God's creation of trees</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:11-Gen1:12\">GEN 1:11–1:12</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Acacia</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:1-Exod37:5\">EXO 37:1–37:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:1-Exod25:16\">EXO 25:1–25:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:23\">EXO 25:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:15\">EXO 26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:26\">EXO 26:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:1\">EXO 27:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:6\">EXO 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:1\">EXO 30:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:36\">EXO 36:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:25\">EXO 37:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:1\">EXO 38:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:3\">DEU 10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:19\">ISA 41:19</a></p>\n<h2>Almond tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:11-Jer1:12\">JER 1:11–1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:37-Gen30:39\">GEN 30:37–30:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:31-Exod25:34\">EXO 25:31–25:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:17-Exod37:20\">EXO 37:17–37:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:5\">ECC 12:5</a></p>\n<h2>Almug-wood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:11-1Kgs10:12\">1KI 10:11–10:12</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Balsam tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:22-2Sam5:25\">2SA 5:22–5:25</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:13-1Chr14:16\">1CH 14:13–14:16</a></p>\n<h2>Broom tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:4\">JOB 30:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:3–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps120:4\">PSA 120:4</a></p>\n<h2>Cedar tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:3\">EZK 31:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:33\">1KI 4:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:27\">1KI 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:12-Ps92:15\">PSA 92:12–92:15</a></p>\n<h2>Cypress tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:14\">ISA 44:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:14\">GEN 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:19\">ISA 41:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:13\">ISA 60:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:6\">EZK 27:6</a></p>\n<h2>Fig-tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:4\">MIC 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:7-Deut8:9\">DEU 8:7–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:29-Luke21:31\">LUK 21:29–21:31</a></p>\n<h2>Fir tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:19-Isa41:20\">ISA 41:19–41:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:13\">ISA 60:13</a></p>\n<h2>Myrtle</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:13\">ISA 55:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:19\">ISA 41:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:8-Zech1:11\">ZEC 1:8–1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Oak tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:26\">JOS 24:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:4\">GEN 35:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:8\">GEN 35:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:11-Judg6:19\">JDG 6:11–6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:9-2Sam18:14\">2SA 18:9–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:13-1Kgs13:14\">1KI 13:13–13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:9\">PSA 29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:1\">PSA 56:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:29-Isa1:30\">ISA 1:29–1:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:12-Isa2:13\">ISA 2:12–2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:13\">ISA 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:14\">ISA 44:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:5\">ISA 57:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:3\">ISA 61:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:13\">EZK 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:6\">EZK 27:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:13\">HOS 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:9\">AMO 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech11:2\">ZEC 11:2</a></p>\n<h2>Olive tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:8\">PSA 52:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:8-Judg9:9\">JDG 9:8–9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:1-Zech4:14\">ZEC 4:1–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:24\">ROM 11:24</a></p>\n<h2>Palm tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:9\">NUM 33:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:27\">EXO 15:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:29\">1KI 6:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:5\">2CH 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:12\">PSA 92:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:8\">SNG 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:16\">EZK 40:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:17-Ezek41:20\">EZK 41:17–41:20</a></p>\n<h2>Pine tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:13\">ISA 60:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:15\">1KI 6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:11\">1KI 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:23\">2KI 19:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:24\">ISA 37:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:8\">ISA 14:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:19\">ISA 41:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:13\">ISA 55:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:5\">EZK 27:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:8\">EZK 31:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:8\">HOS 14:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech11:2\">ZEC 11:2</a></p>\n<h2>Plane trees</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:37\">GEN 30:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek31:8\">EZK 31:8</a></p>\n<h2>Poplar tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:4\">ISA 44:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:37\">GEN 30:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:13\">HOS 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Sycamore-fig tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:27\">1KI 10:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:15\">2CH 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:27\">2CH 9:27</a></p>\n<h2>Terebinth tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:13\">ISA 6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:13\">HOS 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Willow tree</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:5-Ezek17:6\">EZK 17:5–17:6</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Great trees</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:18\">GEN 13:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:13\">GEN 14:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:1\">GEN 18:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:30\">DEU 11:30</a></p>\n<h2>Symbolic use of trees</h2>\n<h3>As a symbol of permanence or long life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:22\">ISA 65:22</a></p>\n<h3>As a symbol of well-being</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:3\">PSA 1:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:8\">JER 17:8</a></p>\n<h3>As a means of execution</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:23\">DEU 21:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30\">ACT 5:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:13\">GAL 3:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a></p>\n<h3>As bearers of fruit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:10\">MAT 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:17-Matt7:19\">MAT 7:17–7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:33\">MAT 12:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:43-Luke6:44\">LUK 6:43–6:44</a></p>\n<h3>The trees of life and knowledge</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:9\">GEN 2:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:2\">REV 22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14\">REV 22:14</a></p>\n<h3>As an example of distorted vision</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:24\">MRK 8:24</a></p>",
